query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `posPrintSettings` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  `branchId` int NOT NULL,
  `paperWidth` enum('58mm', '80mm') DEFAULT '80mm' NOT NULL,
  `fontSize` enum('small', 'medium', 'large') DEFAULT 'medium' NOT NULL,
  `showLogo` boolean DEFAULT true NOT NULL,
  `showQRCode` boolean DEFAULT true NOT NULL,
  `showBranchPhone` boolean DEFAULT true NOT NULL,
  `showEmployeeName` boolean DEFAULT true NOT NULL,
  `storeName` varchar(100) DEFAULT 'Symbol AI',
  `storePhone` varchar(20),
  `storeAddress` varchar(200),
  `headerMessage` varchar(200),
  `footerMessage` varchar(200) DEFAULT 'شكراً لزيارتكم ❤',
  `welcomeMessage` varchar(200) DEFAULT 'نتشرف بخدمتكم دائماً',
  `autoPrint` boolean DEFAULT true NOT NULL,
  `printCopies` int DEFAULT 1 NOT NULL,
  `logoUrl` text,
  `createdAt` timestamp DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  `updatedAt` timestamp DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);
